	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Humanissimas tuas literas 23. iunii scriptas accepi ultimo(a?)</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Augusti, doctissime Bullingere.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae quantum mihi animum addidere, quantum inflammarint, ut in functione mea alacris sim et fortis in domino, haud facile dixero: tu huiusmodi calcaribus subinde me instiges oro.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Equo tardigrado admovenda calcaria.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus convertat aut conterat quinque Palaestinorum satrapias, quae piis molestias exhibere non desinunt!</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod <persName ref="p505" cert="high">Burcherus</persName> a putido illo scorto, facto divortio, sit avulsus, gaudeo; quod aliam duxerit, felix illi faustumque sit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <persName ref="p505" cert="high">Burchero</persName> Burcherique rebus ad <persName ref="p505" cert="high">Burcherum</persName> nunc scribo.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ab illo cetera disces.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ubiquitistis meliorem mentem opto, si modo mentem habeant, cum sint et amentes et dementes; quos facile debellabitis tu et dominus <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Martyr</persName>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed novi gloriosorum ingenium.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Victi non cedent; at nisi resipuerint, vincet eos Christus, vinciet et Satanas.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus <persName type="auto_name">Palatinum</persName> <persName type="auto_name">Rheni</persName> et <persName type="auto_name">Hessum</persName> suo spiritu corrob ret, et incolumes diu servet!</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caetera narravit tibi <persName ref="p4491" cert="high">Iulius</persName>, qui fuit multorum non tantum auritus, sed et oculatus testis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Resaluta nostro nomine optimam tuam uxorem, filios, filias, generos, d. <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Martyrem</persName>, d. <persName ref="p1283" cert="high">Gesnerum</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Wolphium</persName> et omnes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mea vos omnes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Raptim, <placeName type="auto_name">Ludhamiae</placeName>, 1 septembris 1561.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName type="auto_name">Ioannes Parkhurstus</persName> <placeName type="auto_name">Nordovicensis</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Omnibus verbi ministris per totam Suffolciam et <persName type="auto_name">Norfolciam</persName> in mandatis dedi, ut tuas conciones in Apocalypsim sibi comparent vel Latine vel Anglice.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In nostram enim vernaculam linguam transtulit <persName type="auto_name">Iohannes Daus</persName>, vir bonus et doctus, ludimoderator in urbe Ypsvico.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iterum vale, et valeant Tigurini.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. Henrico Bullingero.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
